Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.98,0:24:35.97,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.99,0:24:59.99,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,One Step Toward the Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:06.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's because I've heard that the Earth is very pretty when you look at it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:11.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,So I want to become a rocket driver and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:15.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I want to take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.20,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,And when they're on my rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.37,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.36,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'll collect your examination papers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:56.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,There will be a logic test in the afternoon, so make sure to be here an hour early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Mercury, Venus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.44,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Earth, Mars, Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:18.33,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Saturn, Uranus, Neptune, Pluto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.45,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.45,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,KAMOGAWA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.79,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,KAMOGAWA!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What were you looking at instead of paying attention to class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, the stars. I was looking at the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In broad daylight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:47.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa, make sure to come to the teachers' office after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.63,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have some time right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,For this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kamogawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're on cleanup duty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We're all done with our part...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so take care of the rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Since you're always causing us so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...that much shouldn't be a big deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.26,Spica - Secondary,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.85,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna grab some tea first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:19.60,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.02,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Fuchuuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you letting them push all of this on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:36.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, but I'm the one at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:39.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You need to do things more clearly, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't, it's easy to be misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:46.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It bothers me when I see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you trying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:55.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eh. Nevermind, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:06.79,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,1961, the USSR sends up the first manned space flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:11.66,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,1969, Apollo 11 completes man's first landing on the moon's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And also Japan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even studying on the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You stupid lion! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.07,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is that girl making a fuss over all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.24,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That wasn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.47,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't let you catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That wasn't it, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,See, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So you still want to go after all, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,To space school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you used to be an astronaut, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Were the exams really a lot of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:59.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In Japan back then, they had just started training astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, there was no Space Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You would never even think of being an astronaut when you were just a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Day-to-day life hasn't changed much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:23.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...but I guess that just shows how much closer space has gotten for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:28.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Although if that accident hadn't happened,\Nit would have been quicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,More importantly, will it be okay, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:40.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You still haven't talked with your father about it, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:46.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Telling him you want to go to the Space Academy in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.07,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, that old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Working us so hard, this late into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's just curry though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This is the third straight day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, with our finances in this state...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can't compla—{timing?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,M-My back just suddenly... Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if we had an electric massager, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where would we get that kind of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're just the right weight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.32,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you serious about this, Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:08:01.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that I can't understand the desire to be an astronaut, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The astronaut training course was just established...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so you'd be one of the first to go through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:12.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I think it would be a lot of work for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:17.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're the smallest girl in the school, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The tuition for a national school like this can be pretty overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:27.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, how do you plan to attend that school when you live all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:30.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It says that there's a dorm for applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:33.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san, I seem to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:37.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother passed away when you were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and you're living alone with your father right now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:44.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you end up attending this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:48.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...you'll be leaving your father all alone, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:52.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your father wasn't against this idea or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:53.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, he's such a slob!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's on the early shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I guess he really wouldn't be able to do without me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.47,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:52.54,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:59.84,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a rocket driver and take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:04.42,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Moron! You don't say a rocket "driver!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.62,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.12,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Asumi, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.29,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Now, father, please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:19.96,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,And my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:27.47,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Your composition at school was very well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.51,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.74,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:36.61,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.88,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.52,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hm, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.05,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,A present!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.90,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.05,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.88,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.85,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mom is up there too, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:19.89,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Let's go see her together on my rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:23.83,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's. Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.93,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.90,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Right, it's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:36.17,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,If I tell a lie, make me swallow a thousand needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:48.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad says that he actually used to be pretty cool and popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:52.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, he's talking about himself, so you can't be too sure about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When I was little, he always wore a business suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He was a rocket engineer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But now he's such a slob, and sort of insensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:08.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and he always looks tired, so he seems pretty unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Orion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.73,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,In the middle of all those stars, the alpha star, Betelgeuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.90,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Even though it looks so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:34.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...it's actually a huge star, more than 500 times the size of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's called a supergiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:42.91,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If we don't think much about it,\Nwe would never realize how big the star is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.24,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,As long as we can't see it with our own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.45,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...we can't tell how brightly it shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:52.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's the same way with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're home early today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get dinner ready right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in here without the lights on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I got a call from your homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:48.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! Don't go looking at my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:57.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, this doesn't really matter anymore. Let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:13:59.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, it doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:02.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That hurts, Dad! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Say it clearly, Asumi. Why doesn't it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:10.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I just thought I would take it for memory's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:13.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I would see if I could pass it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:16.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I passed, we don't have the money to pay for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:20.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't really thinking of leaving you here alone and going off to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking you about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:24.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be coming home late from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I won't need dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,This sums up all of this year, so make sure to remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.16,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:33.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you giving up on space school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:04.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, I don't know what I should do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad hasn't said much to me since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and he works day and night, only coming home to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But of course, Dad is mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,After all, we don't have the money for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and Dad would be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:27.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, little one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:42.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your father isn't mad at you because you went and took the exam on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:46.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It wasn't because you didn't tell him about it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:49.69,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What your dad couldn't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:55.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...was probably seeing you unable to honestly talk about your dreams anymore, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:17.42,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I want to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.15,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking you about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:25.39,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,…was probably seeing you unable to honestly talk about your dreams anymore, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:32.79,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,If we don't think much about it, we would never realize how big the star is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.16,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,As long as we can't see it with our own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.50,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,...we can't tell how brightly it shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You'll freeze sitting down out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:08.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Heh! Don't treat me like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:11.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's my entire savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:36.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That should be enough for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:40.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I've asked them to give me more work, so we should be able to take care of the school fees somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:42.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:47.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Children shouldn't have to be hesitant around their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:50.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, the two of us only have each other as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:54.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're my one and only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.50,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:02.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If it would help you on your way to happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:06.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:11.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind selling our household goods, the whiskey, the house, or our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I have this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:20.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This thing that you gave to me when you were little, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I have this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:27.54,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Dad, um... Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:28.84,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.74,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,A present!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:39.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, your dream is my most important treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:17.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Number 95, Kamogawa Asumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:19.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:24.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san, why is it that you want to attend this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:27.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:32.59,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Becoming an astronaut has been a dream of mine ever since I was a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.59,0:22:40.40,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,So being admitted to this school would be one step in changing that dream into reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:44.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If I'm admitted, in order to become an astronaut...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.31,0:24:36.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The admissions test for space school is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:41.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Or so I thought, but everyone who passed has to take a secondary exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.40,0:24:45.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,An exam where you have to spend a whole week with a group of three people in one small room!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.69,0:24:49.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In the same room as me, there are two girls who are completely different types.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.95,0:24:53.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What in the world is the objective of this test?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.37,0:24:55.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica: One Step Toward the Stars.